snippet.title: Sneak Peek: Unleash the Power of Mega Kangaskhan and Mega Gyarados!
snippet.description:
Mega Kangaskhan and Mega Gyarados are ready to battle! In Pokémon: Let’s Go, Pikachu! and Pokémon: Let’s Go, Eevee!, you can Mega Evolve these two powerful Pokémon to unlock their full potential. http://bit.ly/2wbwP3i

Preorder Pokemon: Let's Go, Pikachu!: http://bit.ly/2zziq5M
Preorder Pokemon: Let's Go, Eevee!: http://bit.ly/2NHUO1I
